sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as MCP Client<br/>(Claude Code / VS Code)
    participant AGW as Agentgateway Proxy
    participant IdP as Identity Provider
    participant API as MCP Server

    rect rgb(243, 240, 255)
    Note over Client,API: 1. Initialization
    Client->>AGW: Connect to MCP server
    AGW-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized + resource metadata endpoint
    end

    rect rgb(223, 247, 233)
    Note over Client,API: 2. Discovery
    Client->>AGW: GET /.well-known/oauth-protected-resource/mcp
    AGW-->>Client: Resource metadata (required scopes)
    Client->>AGW: GET /.well-known/oauth-authorization-server
    AGW->>IdP: Fetch authorization server metadata
    IdP-->>AGW: Auth server endpoints
    AGW-->>Client: Modified metadata (AGW as registration endpoint)
    end

    rect rgb(254, 246, 224)
    Note over Client,API: 3. Dynamic Client Registration
    Client->>AGW: POST /register (redirect_uris)
    AGW->>IdP: Register MCP client
    IdP-->>AGW: client_id
    AGW-->>Client: client_id
    end

    rect rgb(252, 232, 243)
    Note over Client,API: 4. Authentication (OAuth Flow)
    Client->>IdP: Initiate OAuth flow (client_id)
    IdP->>Client: Login page
    Client->>IdP: Submit credentials
    IdP->>Client: Authorization code
    Client->>IdP: Exchange code for token
    IdP->>Client: JWT access token
    end

    rect rgb(224, 236, 255)
    Note over Client,API: 5. MCP Server Access
    Client->>AGW: Connect with Bearer JWT
    AGW->>AGW: Validate JWT (fetch JWKS)
    AGW->>API: Forward authenticated request
    API-->>AGW: Tools, prompts, resources
    AGW-->>Client: MCP response
    end
